  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5256735/" class="title-link">为了忘却的纪忆——评崔永元制造《我的抗战》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5256735"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yebuguoruci/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3319508-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yebuguoruci/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">庞二哥</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-05"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-05 20:50:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5256735_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  	崔永元“制造”的这本《我的抗战》，是电视纪录片《我的抗战》的文字版。文字版和纪录片有两点很大的区别：一是文字版更深入，我们可以看到更多“在片子里没有展开的情节”；二是做成了书之后，有很多细节可以反复看，你可以盯着一段文字或是一幅画面几分钟，任思绪从心头萌生...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5256735_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5256735_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
